<p><a name="Areas" id="Areas"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Nevada_Test_Site&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: Areas">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Areas</span></h2>
<p>The Test Site is broken down into areas. Some of the areas and their uses include the following.</p>
<p><a name="Area_12" id="Area_12"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Nevada_Test_Site&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: Area 12">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Area 12</span></h3>
<p>As of 2008, Area 12 was being used by the <a href="/wiki/Office_of_Secure_Transportation" title="Office of Secure Transportation">Office of Secure Transportation</a> as a secure training facility.<sup id="cite_ref-lkas20081107_5-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-lkas20081107-5" title=""><span>[</span>6<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<p><a name="Gallery" id="Gallery"></a></p>
