<li><a href="http://rex.nci.nih.gov/massmedia/Fallout/contents.html" class="external text" title="http://rex.nci.nih.gov/massmedia/Fallout/contents.html" rel="nofollow"><i>Study Estimating Thyroid Doses of I-131 Received by Americans From Nevada Atmospheric Nuclear Bomb Test</i></a>, <a href="/wiki/National_Cancer_Institute" title="National Cancer Institute">National Cancer Institute</a> (1997)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.vce.com/nts.html" class="external text" title="http://www.vce.com/nts.html" rel="nofollow">Images of the Nevada Test Site</a> on the atomic bomb website</li>
<li>Location maps:
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.ufomind.com/area51/maps/overview/general.jpg" class="external text" title="http://www.ufomind.com/area51/maps/overview/general.jpg" rel="nofollow">Small map</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.desertsecrets.com/ntscolormap.html" class="external text" title="http://www.desertsecrets.com/ntscolormap.html" rel="nofollow">Detailed map showing the individual areas</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="http://alsos.wlu.edu/qsearch.aspx?browse=places/Nevada+Test+Site,+Nevada" class="external text" title="http://alsos.wlu.edu/qsearch.aspx?browse=places/Nevada+Test+Site,+Nevada" rel="nofollow">Annotated bibliography for the Nevada Test Site from the Alsos Digital Library for Nuclear Issues</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.sltrib.com/arts/ci_10849700" class="external text" title="http://www.sltrib.com/arts/ci_10849700" rel="nofollow">'Exposed' spreads anti-nuke message</a></li>
</ul>
